#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfcinv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.erfcinv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:1 of
msgid "Inverse of the complementary error function."
msgstr "互补误差函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:3 of
msgid "Computes the inverse of the complementary error function."
msgstr "计算互补误差函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:5 of
msgid ""
"In the complex domain, there is no unique complex number w satisfying "
"erfc(w)=z. This indicates a true inverse function would be multivalued. "
"When the domain restricts to the real, 0 < x < 2, there is a unique real "
"number satisfying erfc(erfcinv(x)) = erfcinv(erfc(x))."
msgstr ""
"在复数域中，不存在唯一的复数 w 满足 erfc(w)=z。这表明真正的反函数将是多值"
"的。当定义域限制在实数范围 0 < x < 2 内时，存在唯一的实数满足 erfc("
"erfcinv(x)) = erfcinv(erfc(x))。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:10 of
msgid "It is related to inverse of the error function by erfcinv(1-x) = erfinv(x)"
msgstr "它与误差函数的反函数的关系为 erfcinv(1-x) = erfinv(x)"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfcinv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:12 of
msgid "Argument at which to evaluate. Domain: [0, 2]"
msgstr "用于计算的参数。定义域：[0, 2]"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:14 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfcinv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:17 of
msgid "**erfcinv** -- The inverse of erfc of y, element-wise"
msgstr "**erfcinv** -- y 的 erfc 的反函数，逐元素计算"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfcinv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:23 of
msgid "Error function of a complex argument"
msgstr "复数参数的误差函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erfc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:26 of
msgid "Complementary error function, ``1 - erf(x)``"
msgstr "互补误差函数，``1 - erf(x)``"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erfinv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfcinv:29 of
msgid "Inverse of the error function"
msgstr "误差函数的反函数"

